Title: One step away from everything
DateModified: '2018-02-12'
DatePublished: '2018-04-20'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2018/applications/one-step-away-from-everything
SetInCountry: India
Category: The last thing I expected
AuthorName: Hemalatha Sekar
AuthorCountry: India
Text: Being a girl from a conservative background in a metropolitan city has been
  a life of oxymoron. The first time I travelled farthest within the country was when
  I was 23 years old. My travel story thus would be matured and out-sprung drive and
  would bring the best in me.
